eive.</p><h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2><h3>What is a poker bonus?</h3><p>A poker bonus is usually an online bonus given to players to play <a href="/poker-games/" target="_blank">poker games</a> on a website. Once the bonus is credited to your account, you can use it to play almost any poker games you like. We have a variety types of bonuses available to all our players.</p><h3>What kinds of poker bonuses are available?</h3><p>At 888poker we have all different types of online bonuses available:</p><h4>Free and no-deposit bonuses</h4><p>We have completely free, no deposit needed bonuses, such as our registration offer. You don’t need to make any deposit or make any payment in order to receive such a free bonus.</p><h4>Deposit bonus</h4><p>There are deposit bonuses, which are either a percentage or a flat amount given upon the player making a deposit. At 888poker you choose the deposit bonus you want to receive by entering the promo code when you make the deposit.</p><h4>Rake-back bonus</h4><p>We also offer rake back bonuses. A rake back is a percentage of a player’s rake, issued back to him after playing. For example, you might be offered a special rake back on all your rake from a certain day, or all your rake on a certain poker game over a specific time period.</p><p></p></div> </div></div> </div></div>               </div>      </div> </div></div>               </div>      </div> </div></div><?php include_once ($_SERVER["DOCUMENT_ROOT"]."/footer.php"); ?>